@startuml
skinparam Style strictuml
skinparam SequenceMessageAlignment center

actor "Пользователь" as User
participant "Mobile UI" as UI
participant "Finance API" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Analytics Service" as Analytics
participant "Notification Service" as Push

User -> UI: Вводит сумму дохода (1000 руб.)
UI -> API: POST /api/income {amount: 1000, idempotency_key: "uuid"}
activate API

note right of API: Начало транзакции распределения
API -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION

API -> DB: SELECT categories WHERE user_id = ? (проценты)
activate DB
DB --> API: [ {id:1, name: "Еда", pct: 60}, {id:2, name: "Спорт", pct: 40} ]
deactivate DB

API -> API: Расчет долей (600 руб. и 400 руб.)

API -> DB: INSERT INTO transactions (type: income, total: 1000)
API -> DB: UPDATE category_balances SET sum = sum + 600 WHERE id = 1
API -> DB: UPDATE category_balances SET sum = sum + 400 WHERE id = 2

API -> DB: COMMIT TRANSACTION
activate DB
DB --> API: OK (Transaction Committed)
deactivate DB

API --> UI: 201 Created (Успешно распределено)
deactivate API

UI --> User: Показать уведомление: "1000 руб. зачислено"

== Асинхронные операции (Eventual Consistency) ==

note over API, Analytics: Обновление отчетов происходит в фоне
API --[#blue]> Analytics: Event: IncomeDistributed {txn_id: 123}
activate Analytics
Analytics -> DB: Пересчет агрегатов для графиков
deactivate Analytics

note over API, Push: Отправка уведомления пользователю
API --[#blue]> Push: Command: SendPushNotification {user_id: 7, msg: "Баланс обновлен"}
activate Push
Push -> User: Push: "Зачислено 600 на Еду и 400 на Спорт"
deactivate Push

@enduml